msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/dev-ui.adoc
msgid "Lastly, you can add pages that is not listed anywhere, but added to the Router, and can be navigated to. This is useful if you are building very complex pages that navigates to more pages."
