#: _versions/3.34/guides/dev-ui.adoc
msgid "Then create the component alongside your other Dev UI pages:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/dev-ui.adoc
msgid "The `namespace` attribute will always be provided automatically by Dev UI."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/dev-ui.adoc
